How to Use This Script:

Set Your Thresholds: Adjust the IMPRESSIONS_THRESHOLD, CLICKS_THRESHOLD, CTR_THRESHOLD, and CR_THRESHOLD variables at the top to match the minimum acceptable values for your campaigns.
Set Your Email Address: Replace 'your-email@example.com' with your actual email address where you want to receive the alerts.

Add the Script to Google Ads:
 Go to your Google Ads account.
 Click on Tools and Settings > Scripts.
 Create a new script
